      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一美人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么多人，都是找我的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们似乎是约集齐了来找展小侠，雷大叔说展小侠不在，他们不信，要挨屋搜查，'穷家帮'的人出面拦阻，他们已出手伤了人，而且声言不寻出展小侠，要把在场所有之人，一一杀死……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有这等事，我去看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南二奇",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "直上青云",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南二奇",
